@host = {{host}}
@token = {{token}}
@userId = {{userId}}

### Resumen MAC del usuario — clearance + compartimentos
# Hace: `GET .../user-authorizations/{user}/` devuelve `user_id`, `clearance` (null si no tiene) y `compartments`.

GET {{host}}/api/v1/user-authorizations/{{userId}}/
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
